2014;;The Dependables;;Canadian;;Sidney J. Furie;;Seymour Cassel, Margot Kidder, Bo Svenson;;action, comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Dependables;;Five young American soldiers are held hostage in Afghanistan by a Taliban warlord. When the US Army is slow to act, a grandmother and four grandfathers with military backgrounds fly to Afghanistan to rescue them.[1]